623
00:25:31,225 --> 00:25:33,836
[suspira] Sério, Jin?

624
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:35,142
Você tem algo a dizer?

625
00:25:35,185 --> 00:25:37,274
Sim. Magnum e Higgins

626
00:25:37,318 --> 00:25:39,668
